                "text": "Before making an attack with a weapon, a scholar of magic can spend 1 Resolve Point and expend a spell slot or spell gem to gain a circumstance bonus to the attack equal to half the spell\u2019s level and a bonus to the attack\u2019s damage equal to 3 \u00d7 the spell\u2019s level. ",
